程序包 P2V

类 VLine

java.lang.Object
P2V.VObj
P2V.VLine
public class VLine extends VObj
VLine is a class that represents a line visual object in the application. It extends the VObj abstract class and inherits its properties and methods. However, some methods or properties are not available or readonly in VImg, such as Fill, Widt, Heit and so on.
作者:
Telsa

  • 字段详细资料

    • PosiE

      protected VXy PosiE
      Represents the position of the second point (end point) of the VLine object. This point defines the other end of the line. In VLine, Posi represents the first end of the line.

    • VLine

      public VLine(float sx, float sy, float ex, float ey, float stroWei, int a, int r, int g, int b)
      Creates a new VLine object with the specified start and end points represented by the given coordinates, stroke weight, and stroke color.
      参数:
      sx - The x-coordinate of the start point.
      sy - The y-coordinate of the start point.
      ex - The x-coordinate of the end point.
      ey - The y-coordinate of the end point.
      stroWei - The stroke weight of the line.
      a - The alpha value of the stroke color.
      r - The red value of the stroke color.
      g - The green value of the stroke color.
      b - The blue value of the stroke color.
